The paper deals with web archiving, summarizing holdings of web archives, and evaluating the accuracy of the summaries. This work involves information retrieval (IR) techniques such as indexing and searching, as well as data management (DB) and data structures (DL) for efficient storage and retrieval of large amounts of data. The paper also discusses the behavior of web archives and the design of user interfaces (HC) for accessing archived content. Finally, the paper touches on security and privacy concerns (CR) related to web archiving.
